%^YELLOW%^Skill: Dungeoneering

%^BOLD%^%^WHITE%^A player's dungeoneering skill indicates their understanding of mechanical items, and other intricate constructions. This will usually involve dealing with a variety of locks and rigged traps, both in recognizing and dismantling them.

%^BOLD%^%^CYAN%^Stat basis: %^WHITE%^dexterity
%^BOLD%^%^CYAN%^Current areas of influence: %^WHITE%^finding and removing traps, picking locks

%^BOLD%^%^CYAN%^Related helpfiles: %^WHITE%^skills, trap
